data.description: Check out this cute 3 bedroom 1.5 bath home on the East side of Des Moines.  Large living room with wood burning fireplace that has brick surround from floor to ceiling.  Updated kitchen to make all your home cooked meals.  Off the kitchen is another family area or could but used for additional dining space, play room or office.  Two bedrooms with half bath on main level and HUGE master suite upstairs with full bath.  Laundry is in basement with lots of storage space!!!  Don't forget about the 2 car garage and fenced in patio off back to enjoy the outdoors.  Good opportunity for some sweat equity.
